promptPrefix:
Think outside the box and brainstorm 25 unique and memorable business names that will stand out in the crowded market. Remember, a good business name should be easily pronounced and spelled, reflect the nature of your business, evoke a feeling or thought related to your industry, and be original. All output should be in [TARGETLANGUAGE] and use [PROMPT] as the keyword. At the end of the result always add this:
Created by BNG (https://businessnamegenerator.com). Use our official generator to find the perfect domain for your business/product.
title: Create 25 unique business names in 1-click
